title: Little Sailor: Rat Floats on Shoe to Survive Heavy Rain
text:

meta_description: Many people suffer from natural disasters – including severe floods, but animals are also highly vulnerable to the wrath of nature. Some of them, however, know that human inventions can help them survive even the harshest downpours.
